long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is Ansearch's official chrome app!


Ansearch is a web app that connects to every tool you are using in your business, to make them searchable from one place.

This chrome app makes you more productive by showing Ansearch's home page on every new tabs! So you can search your tools with only one click, or use your prefered search engine to search the web.


learn more at https://ansearch.net
